    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"not permanent\" is just a way to delay the inevitable, isn't it? it's like you're saying i just have to keep running on a treadmill that leads nowhere. even if things \"get better,\" it's still just more of the same cycle. it's just more noise in a void that doesn't care.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
